==Administration==
Since 2015, Rennes is divided into 6 [[Canton in France|cantons]] (populations as of 2014):&lt;ref name=decret&gt;[http://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/affichTexte.do?cidTexte=JORFTEXT000028637230 Décret n° 2014-177 du 18 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département d'Ille-et-Vilaine]&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;[https://www.insee.fr/fr/statistiques/fichier/2525755/dep35.pdf INSEE 2014 legal populations of the Ille-et-Vilaine department]&lt;/ref&gt;
* [[Canton of Rennes-1]] (38,672 inhabitants)
* [[Canton of Rennes-2]] (40,124 inhabitants)
* [[Canton of Rennes-3]], which includes parts of Rennes but also the ''commune'' of [[Chantepie]] (43,829 inhabitants)
* [[Canton of Rennes-4]] (37,036 inhabitants)
* [[Canton of Rennes-5]], which includes parts of Rennes but also the ''commune'' of [[Saint-Jacques-de-la-Lande]] (43,072 inhabitants)
* [[Canton of Rennes-6]], which includes parts of Rennes but also the ''commune'' of [[Pacé, Ille-et-Vilaine|Pacé]] (44,888 inhabitants)

[[File:Plan quartiers Rennes.svg|thumb|right|Rennes quarters]]

Rennes is divided into 12 [[Quarter (country subdivision)|quarters]]:
