# Sud Gare
# Cleunay-Arsenal-Redon
# Villejean-Beauregard
# Le Blosne
# Bréquigny

===Mayors===
[[File:Nathalie Appéré - Février 2013 - 05.JPG|thumb|right|[[Nathalie Appéré]], current mayor of Rennes]]
The current mayor of Rennes is [[Nathalie Appéré]]. A member of the [[Socialist Party (France)|Socialist Party]], she replaced retiring [[Socialist Party (France)|Socialist]] incumbent [[Daniel Delaveau]], in office from 2008 to 2014.
